{"tid":518721,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"經理要我地班女仔陪老細食飯，想整番鍋勁野比佢嘆","createTime":"2018-01-03T15:33:24.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-03T16:40:42.000Z","uid":135446,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"d572eb23d1b96d01a2b35bb7758c31df245ea5b6","tid":518721,"uid":135446,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-03T15:33:24.000Z","msg":"是咁的，上年新入左間公司做野，大陸廠，香港公司咁樣。<br />\n<br />\n好多濕尻公司文化，其中令我最慶既係經理定時要我地部門既女仔同老板食飯，重點係條老淫蟲會攬同錫。<br />\n<br />\n第一次去唔知，屌佢老味<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n去到先知係鴻門宴<br />\n<br />\n好啦，想年尾攞完雙糧走人，點知個仆街經理又安排多一次飯局，仲攞d雙糧要脅我地<br />\n<br />\nPs 入職無合約<br />\n<br />\n依家想集思廣益，諗辦法整鑊野比佢嘆，法律行動會照做，但想整死佢先<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b95f2ab2808a2a8ee4618abb4b71a36785e0212","tid":518721,"uid":142532,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-03T15:36:00.000Z","msg":"整鍋勁野 我以為真係煮野食比佢"},{"pid":"99abd3202cabb661db346f5c22fc2384f5473c1f","tid":518721,"uid":135446,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6b95f2ab2808a2a8ee4618abb4b71a36785e0212","tid":518721,"uid":142532,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-03T15:36:00.000Z","msg":"整鍋勁野 我以為真係煮野食比佢"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-03T15:38:49.000Z","msg":"比屎佢食就得"},{"pid":"d3b7ea5e961dd174045b12e1e6c43d11f588786c","tid":518721,"uid":15371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-03T16:35:08.000Z","msg":"最緊要係個鍋"},{"pid":"32cb4528070d79646cdea28f692ef0a0fe99bbfb","tid":518721,"uid":110832,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-03T16:38:52.000Z","msg":"拍片錄音唔少得啦"},{"pid":"2f6ff3dacb4434e1b5d909dd6d303ab4f1df0829","tid":518721,"uid":161907,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-03T16:40:27.000Z","msg